anna County, Virginia|Fluvanna County]]\n|4\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Franklin, Virginia|Franklin (city)]]\n|1\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Franklin County, Virginia|Franklin (city)]]\n|6\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Frederick County, Virginia|Frederick County]]\n|16\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Fredericksburg, Virginia|Fredericksburg (city)]]\n|2\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Galax, Virginia|Galax (city)]]\n|1\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Gloucester County, Virginia|Gloucester County]]\n|8\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Goochland County, Virginia|Goochland County]]\n|9\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Greene County, Virginia|Greene County]]\n|1\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Greensville, Virginia|Greensville (city)]]\n|3\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Halifax County, Virginia|Halifax County]]\n|1\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Hampton, Virginia|Hampton (city)]]\n|16\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Hanover County, Virginia|Hanover County]]\n|8\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Harrisonburg, Virginia|Harrisonburg (city)]]\n|10\n|0\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" |[[Henrico County, Virginia|Henrico County]]\n|87\n|8<ref>{{cite web |title=COVID-19 in Virginia: LIVE updates for Sunday, March 29 - Henrico nursing home COVID-19 outbreak: 37 positive, 8 dead |url=https://www.wtvr.com/news/coronavirus/covid-19-in-virginia-live-updates-for-sunday-march-29 |website=www.wtvr.com |publisher=[[WTVR-TV]] |accessdate=March 30, 2020 |date=March 29, 2020}}</ref><ref name=\"WSLS-March 24\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.wsls.com/news/local/2020/03/24/two-elderly-virginians-are-states-8th-9th-coronavirus-deaths/|title=Two elderly Virginians are state's 8th, 9th coronavirus deaths|website=WSLS10|language=en-US|access-date=2020-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325035022/https://www.wsls.com/news/local/2020/03/24/two-elderly-virginians-